OL,5, Rare footage obtained by BBC Korean    
OL,6, shows North Korea publicly sentencing  
OL,7, two teenage boys to 12 years of hard   
OL,8, labour for watching K-dramas.          
OL,10,FThe footage, which appears to have been
OL,11,Ffilmed in 2022, shows two 16-year-old  
OL,12,Fboys handcuffed in front of hundreds of
OL,13,Fstudents at an outdoor stadium.        
OL,15,FIt also shows uniformed officers       
OL,16,Freprimanding the boys for not "deeply  
OL,17,Freflecting on their mistakes".         
OL,19,FSouth Korean entertainment, including  
OL,20,FTV, is banned in the North.            
